From: Wenjing Liu <Wenjing.Liu@amd.com>
Date: Mon, 13 Jan 2020 17:05:42 -0500
Subject: drm/amd/display: use odm combine for YCbCr420 timing with h_active
Git-commit: d478667253f988dbd6215734a11e35f6953b540d
Patch-mainline: v5.6-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322
 greater than 4096

[why]
FMT has limitation to support YCbCr420 with h_active greater than 4096.

[how]
Use odm combine to overcome the limitation.

Signed-off-by: Wenjing Liu <Wenjing.Liu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: Dmytro Laktyushkin <Dmytro.Laktyushkin@amd.com>
Acked-by: Bhawanpreet Lakha <Bhawanpreet.Lakha@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
